{
  "stem": "18102.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 259.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the mayor advised the council members, Jew and non-Jew alike, that when the Germans would take over Bialystock, which was expected to happen, they would then arrest all the council members and use them as hostages, should anything go wrong in the city.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Should there be any violent protest or argument with the-- with the German army, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they would use those hostages to shoot them, 10 at a time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And therefore, the mayor advised that all the council personnel and-- and city councilmen should leave before the Germans entered the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that, in fact, is what my father decided to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That wasn't till much later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you like, I'll go into that whole history, but it-- it was quite a number of weeks later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, maybe a month later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What-- what happened was, of course, that my father, on one evening, I was awoken in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother escorted me to a lot where there was this big van waiting with a lot of people milling around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was 3:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the way there, I remember the-- the sounds of the bombs and the [INAUDIBLE] fire that echoed through the buildings as we walked in Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said my goodbyes to my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, it was a very tearful event, as you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A lot of people there saying goodbye to all the other councilmen that were leaving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother and I stayed behind, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Germans entered the city of Bialystok a few days later.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
